descriptions.value: A cheap option for cash-strapped players, the FAMAS effectively fills the niche between more expensive rifles and the less-effective SMGs. It has been painted in a marbleized pattern.

The CT-exclusive Mag-7 delivers a devastating amount of damage at close range. Its rapid magazine-style reloads make it a great tactical choice. It has been painted using an urban Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic over a metallic base coat.
This item commemorates the 2018 ELEAGUE Boston CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Group Stage match between SK Gaming and Gambit Esports, and autographed by Dauren Kystaubayev who was the most valuable player in that round.

Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a stormy color scheme. It will be waiting for you at the monorail
Sticker: SK Gaming (Gold) | Boston 2018, ELEAGUE (Gold) | Boston 2018, AdreN (Gold) | Boston 2018, Gambit Esports (Gold) | Boston 2018
